rows.label: tev900301_MSG0010
rows.name:
So, looks like I'm Vandham's gopher now.
I've been back, what, five minutes? Dang.
...Anyway, guessing you need a hand?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900301_MSG0040
rows.name:
Okey-doke, time to roll up the ol' sleeves.
I'm not getting any younger.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900301_MSG0070
rows.name:
That's a-okay by me. In the meantime,
I'm gonna go catch some z's. Later![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900301_MSG0080
rows.name:
...What's up?
Pressure finally gettin' to you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900301_MSG0090
rows.name:
I've been there before, lemme tell you.
Well, if you need someone to share the
load, I'm here for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900301_MSG0150
rows.name:
This could be the one. The biggest
moment of your life. You won't be at
your best unless you rest, so rest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900301_MSG0160
rows.name:
Void took Earth from us. Now he's
taken NLA... That's twice, now. Twice
the bastard's destroyed our home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900301_MSG0170
rows.name:
That ends here.
This time, he's the one getting a bruising.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev900301_MSG0180
rows.name:
How's about we win this damn fight
already and claim the future we were
always meant to have?![ST:wait ]
